.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH devin-shell 1  "shell " 
.SH NAME
devin\-shell \- [Feature preview] Integrate with your shell to instantly launch devin with relevant context
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin shell\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
[Feature preview] Integrate with your shell to instantly launch devin with relevant context
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
devin\-shell\-init(1)
Output shell integration script for eval
.TP
devin\-shell\-run(1)
Run the shell wrapper
.TP
devin\-shell\-setup(1)
Install shell integration into config files
.TP
devin\-shell\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
